"Slag!" GUILEDART sdaid as he shook his weapon, the webbing from
BLACKARACNIA getting into the nooks and crannies of it. He was trying
to rip it off so he could fire back at the PREDACON!

"Wait!" KILLPUNCH said as he looked around and blinked.

GUILEDART glanced irritably at KILLPUNCH as he tried to get the
webbing off of his weapon. "What?"

Pulling out a small device KILLPUNCH waved it around. "The field, it's
destabizing." He said.

GUILEDART nodded, "Those Maximals were good for something after all."
He said as he looked over at BLACKARACHNIA. "Maybe these Predacons
were not needed."

BAZOOKA who was just starting to recover from the paralytic that
BLACKARACHNIA had hit him with. "Whaatt? I will slaaayy heer with my
own haandds."

BAZOOKA was sluring his words still as he fought to stand.

GUILEDART looked at BLACKARACHNIA, "No Bazooka, we have other things
to do like get our leader back."

Looking at BLACKARAHCNIA there was a nod from BAZOOKA as he responded
to GUILEDART.

"We will let you live." BAZOOKA said to BLACKARACHNIA as he was slowly
straightening.

(TAG)
